Package com.github.dandelion.datatables.extras.spring3.ajax

Class Summary
DatatablesCriteriasMethodArgumentResolver Resolves a method argument of type DatatablesCriterias annotated with DatatablesParams.
DatatablesCriteriasResolver Deprecated. in favor of the DatatablesCriteriasMethodArgumentResolver for versions of Spring 3.1 and greater.
 

Annotation Types Summary
DatatablesParams Annotation used to indicated Spring to resolve the method argument using the DatatablesCriteriasResolver.
